{"tid":1082824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"29歲女子逃離護理院 繩斷墮地大叫：死都唔返上去","createTime":"2019-03-29T08:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T08:40:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"594d2670cc77a9d546ac5c14ec9df7896f606dfa","tid":1082824,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553842997_ba99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553842997_ba99.jpg&h=9bec8005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵涌禾塘咀街109至115號萬成大廈，早上8時13分，一名年約30歲女子，約在8米高簷篷墮下，倒卧在大廈對開地面。有目擊者指，女傷者當時眼鏡甩脫，其後自己拾回戴起，並喃喃自語：「死都唔返上去！」稍後由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，上址二及三樓為一所護理院，姓莫（29歲）女事主是該處的院友。事發時有人在二樓打開窗爬出簷篷，其間跌落地面；警方調查後相信莫女有感情問題。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊的街坊表示，重約160磅、身材較胖的女事主用尼龍繩、插蘇電線及膠喉自製繩索，綁在食肆外牆招牌的電線膠槽位，企圖由簷篷游繩徐徐而下，疑中途繩索斷裂，離地不遠便已失手墮下，當時地下餐廳一名食客聽到巨響，往外查看發現女事主倒地，急忙問她何事，並欲通知其家人，但女事主頻說：「我死都唔返上去，唔使通知屋企人，唔使通知（護理院）。」食客為她報警求助，並送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=ae1df07c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553828110_85b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553828110_85b1.jpg&h=40c43e44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子由二樓護理院窗口爬出，攀到簷篷，綁繩在食肆外牆招牌的電線膠槽位（箭咀所示）游繩而下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553825306_a263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553825306_a263.jpg&h=50561cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553822454_6643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553822454_6643.jpg&h=a4c970ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553825306_1c89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553825306_1c89.jpg&h=273cebf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190329/59424948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59424948&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=daafa50a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59424948&h=0e39059c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190329/59424948</a>"},{"pid":"14b53d87ae3f284a9611a46d8c237c93dee4fcf6","tid":1082824,"uid":95637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"160磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61da9425941d665b88b5defcc91a9b1fc22e2b07","tid":1082824,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有目擊的街坊表示，重約160磅、身材較胖的女事主用尼龍繩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f6ed335cbc474d4ad975ea7a84a7cc056e6096","tid":1082824,"uid":4661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:19:08.000Z","msg":"29歲住老人院<img src=\"/as